{"tid":912404,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"lenovo notebook 永不再錄用","createTime":"2018-11-22T15:43:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T02:20:18.000Z","uid":192880,"like":38,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"04f9fefcc743f83d54a17ac55c36f28c8ecf989a","tid":912404,"uid":192880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T15:43:10.000Z","msg":"跟U買 非thinkpad<br />\n3年壞左4次 次次都直情入唔到window🌞<br />\n次次去整都話我壞hd🌞清晒我d嘢<br />\n但有時我整完根本冇用過 放左係枱 根本唔會震到佢<br />\n<br />\n舊電用唔夠半個鐘就收皮🌞我一定要叉住用<br />\n(當年我以爲呢個款本來係咁 後尾發現同款用到3hr🤯)<br />\n<br />\n今年10月就過咗保養 lm睇幾時再壞<br />\n啱啱usb收左皮 成份fyp冇l左 睇下幾時收埋我隻hd皮😪<br />\n當一個人 真係可以頭頭碰著黑💀<br />\n<br />\n有冇人用lenovo機都係咁？<br />\n客服d人永遠幫唔到你☠️"},{"pid":"d57ebd406bda126ff08af182dda271dfcae41e32","tid":912404,"uid":30836,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T15:46:49.000Z","msg":"跟U買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d08e7ac4f9abd8b13b9c20b294725f6a7b4b4c","tid":912404,"uid":117664,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T15:51:41.000Z","msg":"換左個hd做ssd之後, 用左七年<br />\n仲用緊"},{"pid":"10667eafb48c8a24d59e7bc550e012631dca448d","tid":912404,"uid":58928,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"買lenovo就預咗啦"},{"pid":"c697d84eaaa31e9fae74c7dc02fc5dfdbf428f7d","tid":912404,"uid":84415,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T16:09:36.000Z","msg":"支那貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb4f17071bb5c2926d9f09af96d779dd7e4f093","tid":912404,"uid":194398,"like":13,"dislike":12,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T17:44:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"426290b3a031e01fb17bb5b3e87c8d219dd846a5","tid":912404,"uid":192880,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"6fb4f17071bb5c2926d9f09af96d779dd7e4f093","tid":912404,"uid":194398,"like":13,"dislike":12,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T17:44:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆